headline: Valero Record Quarter Highlights Venezuelan Crude Shift And Project Progress
summary: Valero Energy reported record operating and financial performance for Q4 2025, supported by refining margins and throughput. The company increased purchases of Venezuelan crude following changes in U.S. sanctions policy, adjusting its feedstock mix. Management highlighted ongoing optimization initiatives and ethanol expansion projects across the portfolio.
